\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 1}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
The International Centre for Expertise (the "Centre") is a service centre of the International Chamber of Commerce (ICC). The Centre can perform one or more of the following functions in connection with domestic or international business matters:}{
\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 A) Proposal of experts}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 Upon the request of any physical or legal person(s) or any court or tribunal (a "Person"), the Centre can provide the name of one or more experts in a particu
lar field of activity, pursuant to Section II of these Rules. The Centre's role is limited to proposing the name of one or more experts. The Person requesting a proposal may then contact directly the proposed expert(s), and, as the case may be, agree with
 
such expert(s) on the scope of the appropriate mission and fees. There is no obligation to make use of the services of an expert proposed by the Centre. The proposal of an expert may be useful in many different contexts. A person may require an expert in 
c
onnection with its ongoing business activities or in connection with contractual relations. A party to an arbitration may wish to obtain the name of a potential expert witness. A court or arbitral tribunal which has decided to appoint an expert may seek a
 proposal from the Centre.}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 B) Appointment of experts}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 The Centre will appoint an expert, pursuant to Section III of these Rules, in situations where the 
parties have agreed to the appointment of an expert and have agreed to use the Centre as the appointing authority or where the Centre is otherwise satisfied that there is a sufficient basis for appointing an expert. In such cases the appointment by the Ce
ntre shall be binding on the parties. The Centre's role is limited to appointing the expert in question.}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 C) Administration of expertise proceedings}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 When the parties have agreed upon the administration of expertise proceedings by the Centre or when the Cen
tre is otherwise satisfied that there is a sufficient basis for administering expertise proceedings, the Centre will administer the proceedings pursuant to Section IV of these Rules.
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 2}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 The Centre consists of a Standing Committee and a Secretariat which i
s provided by ICC. The statutes of the Standing Committee are set forth in Appendix I.
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 SECTION II}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004  - }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 PROPOSAL OF EXPERTS}{
\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\b\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 Article 2{\*\bkmkstart art2}{\*\bkmkend art2}
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 Recourse to the Centre
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 1}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
Any Person may ask the Centre to propose one or more experts by submitting a request for proposal of experts (the "Request for Proposal") to the Centre at the ICC International Secretariat in Paris.}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
\par 2}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 The Request for Proposal shall include:}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 a) the name,
 address, telephone and facsimile numbers and e-mail address of each Person filing the Request for Proposal;}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 b) a statement that the requesting Person is seeking the proposal of an expert by the Centre;}{
\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 c) a description of the field of activity of the ex
pert to be proposed along with any desired qualifications of the expert, including but not limited to education, language skills and professional experience, and any undesired attributes of the expert;}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 d) a description of any matters which would disqualify a potential expert; and}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 e) a description of the work to be carried out by the expert and the desired time frame for completing such work.}{
\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
\par 3}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 Unless requested to do so by the person seeking the proposal of an expert, the Centre will not notify any other person of the filing of a Request for Proposal.
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid871004 {\b\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 Article 3{\*\bkmkstart art3}{\*\bkmkend art3}
