Any request for the appointment of an expert (the "Request for Appointment") shall be submitted to the Centre at the ICC International Secretariat in Paris. Any such request shall be processed by the Centre only when it is based upon an agreem
ent between the parties for the appointment of an expert by the Centre or when the Centre is otherwise satisfied that there is a sufficient basis for appointing an expert.
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 2}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 
The date on which the Request for Appointment is received by the Centre shall, for all purposes, be deemed to be the date of the commencement of the agreed or required expertise.
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 3}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 . }{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 The Request for Appointment shall include:}{\f1\fs20\insrsid871004 
\par 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid871004 {\f1\fs20\insrsid871004\charrsid871004 a) the name, address, telepho
